page.title: 02MY HOUSE BY LISA CUNNINGHAM
page.content: OUR BUNGALOW IS DETACHED.MY DAD STARTED TO BUILD IT IN 1967 AND FINISHED IT IN 1969.MY FAMILY HAS BEEN LIVING IN IT FOR 16 YEARS.ITS WALLS ARE BRICKS AND THE ROOF IS TILES.IN THE GARDEN WE HAVE A FISH POND.AROUND THE POND THERE ARE CONCRETE SLABS.DAD HAS GOT A BIG VEGETABLE PATCH.THERE IS A GREENHOUSE NEAR THE VEGETABLE PATCH.ON THE LAWN WE HAVE A CLIMBING FRAME.WE HAVE TWO RABBIT HUTCHES AND BESIDE THEM IS A WENDY HOUSE.WE HAVE A GARAGE WHICH IS NOT JOINED ON TO THE HOUSE.BEHIND THE FISH POND THERE IS A WALL.WE HAVE GATES UP TO STOP THE DOG GETTING OUT.WE ALSO HAVE A GATE NEAR THE GARAGE.
